1
00:00:11,530 --> 00:00:13,230
Three years ago,

2
00:00:13,230 --> 00:00:15,460
in March, you drove me out of the Minister's Manor.

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:17,700
In May, the manor was confiscated.

4
00:00:19,130 --> 00:00:21,030
When I woke up in the mass grave,

5
00:00:21,030 --> 00:00:22,660
I had traces of medicine on me.

6
00:00:22,660 --> 00:00:24,300
Those servants who beat me

7
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:25,800
shouted about killing,

8
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:27,500
but clearly held back their strength.

9
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:31,430
I've been thinking about these suspicious points for the past three years.

10
00:00:31,430 --> 00:00:32,360
At that time,

11
00:00:32,759 --> 00:00:35,220
you knew the Minister's Manor was in danger,

12
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:38,260
so you intentionally drove me away, right?

13
00:00:39,460 --> 00:00:40,260
Father.

14
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:43,230
Lu Jingxing is brave and resourceful,

15
00:00:43,230 --> 00:00:44,230
bold yet careful.

16
00:00:44,430 --> 00:00:45,030
Given time,

17
00:00:45,030 --> 00:00:46,690
he will achieve great things.

18
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:48,060
You should leave with him,

19
00:00:48,060 --> 00:00:49,460
while you still can.

20
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:52,300
Since childhood, I have enjoyed

21
00:00:52,300 --> 00:00:55,430
the honor and protection of being the eldest lady of the Shen family.

22
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:58,760
Now, naturally, I must take on the responsibility I should.

23
00:00:59,830 --> 00:01:01,360
Father is a loyal official of the country,

24
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:03,290
and I am a pillar of the Shen family.

25
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,560
I will never desert

26
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:06,960
or betray the family.

27
00:01:07,330 --> 00:01:08,390
If you don't leave,

28
00:01:08,830 --> 00:01:10,960
Lu Jingxing definitely won't either.

29
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:12,600
Are you going to drag him down,

30
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:15,200
and let him be destroyed by this disaster too?

31
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,660
I have my own decision.

32
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:21,600
I definitely won't put him in a dilemma.

33
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:32,259
I have never truly loved you.

34
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:35,229
Seeing how ridiculous you are,

35
00:01:35,229 --> 00:01:36,759
I was just playing with you.

36
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:40,759
How dare you try to kidnap me and elope.

37
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:42,300
Today, I will beat you to death

38
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:44,560
to protect my reputation.

39
00:01:56,060 --> 00:01:57,100
Don't worry, My Lady.

40
00:01:57,100 --> 00:01:59,229
I have paid those two servants heavily.

41
00:01:59,229 --> 00:02:00,400
They know what they are doing.

42
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,060
Lu Jingxing will definitely survive.

43
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:03,830
Go to my room right now

44
00:02:03,830 --> 00:02:05,860
and get my pearl headdress.

45
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:06,860
Pawn it

46
00:02:06,860 --> 00:02:08,229
for wound medicine.

47
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,900
While he is unconscious,

48
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,200
secretly apply the medicine to him.

49
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,400
Don't let him notice.

50
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,200
Three years ago, when the late Emperor was critically ill,

51
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:18,530
he ordered my father to find his illegitimate son among the people,

52
00:02:18,530 --> 00:02:20,500
and personally wrote an edict,

53
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:23,400
ordering my father to read it publicly after finding the little prince.

54
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:26,300
But before my father could find the little prince,

55
00:02:26,300 --> 00:02:27,730
the late Emperor died of illness,

56
00:02:27,730 --> 00:02:29,960
and the current Emperor ascended the throne.

57
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,600
His Majesty learned about the edict

58
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,860
and hinted that my father should hand it over.

59
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:36,720
My father valued promises and absolutely refused.

60
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,800
The Minister's Manor was bound to be implicated.

61
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,460
I intentionally put on an act to drive you away,

62
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:42,590
so that at least one of us could escape.

63
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,800
I bet right.

64
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,360
You really achieved great success.

65
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,730
Didn't you ever think

66
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:52,300
that I'd rather stay with you to live or die together?

67
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:54,360
The man I, Shen Lvyi, choose

68
00:02:55,060 --> 00:02:58,560
would never prioritize romantic feelings over the greater good.

69
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,630
Later, His Majesty really found a reason

70
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:02,260
to throw my father into death row

71
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:04,390
and confiscate the Minister's Manor.

72
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:06,260
To frame my father, Grand Tutor Wei

73
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:07,600
stole the edict.

74
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:09,860
I could only take a risk

75
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,600
and provoked Wei Er a bit.

76
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,700
She really bought me into the Wei Manor.

77
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:16,460
My mother, siblings, and I then settled down in the Wei Manor,

78
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:18,730
bribing servants to set up spies on one hand,

79
00:03:18,730 --> 00:03:20,990
and searching for the edict on the other.

80
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:23,430
So you urged me to propose to Wei Er.

81
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:27,600
Are we going to the storehouse to find the late emperor's edict?

82
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:29,260
I'll go tear down the Grand Tutor's mansion

83
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:30,930
and snatch the edict.

84
00:03:30,930 --> 00:03:31,860
Stop right there.

85
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:32,930
Have you thought about it?

86
00:03:32,930 --> 00:03:34,500
If the edict is opened

87
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:36,600
and it says to pass the throne to the late emperor's illegitimate child,

88
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:39,030
your action would be a betrayal to His Majesty.

89
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,230
I know.

90
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:43,430
His Majesty is already the emperor.

91
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,200
He recognized your worth.

92
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:48,620
Between the emperor's grace and romantic love,

93
00:03:48,930 --> 00:03:51,329
you are putting yourself in a dilemma.

94
00:03:51,329 --> 00:03:53,260
I'm willing to die for His Majesty,

95
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:56,000
willing to be a beast of burden in the next life to repay him.

96
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,160
But in this life,

97
00:03:58,060 --> 00:03:58,860
I choose you.

98
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,530
Even if I, Lu Jingxing, betray the whole world

99
00:04:01,530 --> 00:04:03,130
and face eternal damnation,

100
00:04:03,330 --> 00:04:04,930
I will always choose you,

101
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,300
Shen Luyi.

102
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,100
Let's go.

103
00:04:11,730 --> 00:04:13,330
If we force our way in,

104
00:04:13,330 --> 00:04:14,630
the Grand Tutor might do something desperate,

105
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:16,730
and the edict will likely be destroyed.

106
00:04:16,730 --> 00:04:18,000
We have to find a way

107
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:20,000
to make him hand it over voluntarily.

108
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,600
You say it, I'll do it.

109
00:04:26,130 --> 00:04:27,460
I have a plan.

110
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:28,800
But,

111
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:32,220
it requires the General to show affection to me.

112
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:35,230
Tell me.

113
00:04:35,930 --> 00:04:37,390
Go through fire and water,

114
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,300
I will listen to you.

115
00:04:39,860 --> 00:04:41,560
It requires the General and me

116
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,960
to be affectionate,

117
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:44,260
arousing jealousy,

118
00:04:44,260 --> 00:04:46,060
to draw the snake out of its hole.

119
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:56,930
This is a good method.

120
00:04:57,630 --> 00:04:59,060
I'm good at it.

121
00:05:50,530 --> 00:05:52,130
Why?

122
00:05:52,130 --> 00:05:54,159
I am the wife of General Weibei.

123
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:56,560
Why does Lu Jingxing cast me aside

124
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,260
and only act so lovey-dovey with that lowly concubine?

125
00:05:58,260 --> 00:06:00,300
Maybe that lowly concubine is seducing the General,

126
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:01,900
not letting him come to see you, Madam.

127
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:02,960
Yes.

128
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,000
You are right.

129
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,060
Go,

130
00:06:08,060 --> 00:06:09,130
take the silver

131
00:06:09,130 --> 00:06:11,360
and bribe the maids and servants in Shen Luyi's courtyard.

132
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:14,360
I want to know exactly how she seduces the General every day.

133
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,430
Yes, Miss.

134
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,230
Remember,

135
00:06:21,530 --> 00:06:23,860
report every move in that courtyard to me,

136
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:27,300
especially what the General and that bitch say and do.

137
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,530
In this situation,

138
00:06:38,530 --> 00:06:40,860
the Shen family can only yield to survive.

139
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:43,560
I persuaded my father that night in the death cell.

140
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,400
He promised to take out the edict

141
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:47,000
to please His Majesty,

142
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,600
perhaps he can even be reinstated.

143
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,659
But didn't you say

144
00:06:49,659 --> 00:06:51,390
the edict was missing and lost?

145
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,159
How can it still be taken out?

146
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,620
My father taught me to forge an edict.

147
00:07:07,530 --> 00:07:10,160
Anyway, no one has ever opened and looked at this edict.

148
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:12,630
Who knows what is true and what is fake?

149
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,030
Great.

150
00:07:29,030 --> 00:07:30,660
God is helping me.

151
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:33,330
Shen Luyi, I'll see how you die this time.

152
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:36,860
Prepare the carriage, I'm going back to my maiden home.

153
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:45,830
Looks like the fish took the bait.

154
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,230
With the strategist's brilliant plan,

155
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:50,290
how could this fool not take the bait?

156
00:07:52,030 --> 00:07:53,760
Then shouldn't you go prepare?

157
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,500
I must ask for a reward from the strategist first,

158
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:57,159
so I have the strength to work.

159
00:08:00,130 --> 00:08:01,860
Tonight I...

160
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:06,530
Hurry up.

161
00:08:06,530 --> 00:08:07,160
Okay.
